<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Setcord — Discord Server Management</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');

        :root {
            --bg: #0a0a1a;
            --card: #111128;
            --purple: #7c3aed;
            --purple-light: #a78bfa;
            --green: #10b981;
            --text: #e2e8f0;
            --muted: #64748b;
            --border: #1e1e4a;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Background glow */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: -200px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 800px;
            height: 800px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124,58,237,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        nav {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 60px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .logo span { color: var(--purple-light); }

        nav a {
            color: var(--text);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 9px 22px;
            background: var(--purple);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        nav a:hover { background: #6d28d9; }

        /* Hero */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px 80px;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            background: rgba(124,58,237,0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.4);
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--purple-light);
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 64px);
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -1.5px;
            margin-bottom: 22px;
        }

        h1 span {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa, #7c3aed);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--muted);
            max-width: 520px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 14px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 14px 30px;
            background: var(--purple);
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(124,58,237,0.3);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #6d28d9;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(124,58,237,0.45);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 14px 30px;
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--text);
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            border-color: var(--purple);
            color: var(--purple-light);
        }

        /* Dashboard preview */
        .preview {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .preview-window {
            background: var(--card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 14px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 40px 100px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
        }

        .window-bar {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            background: #0d0d22;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; }
        .dot.red { background: #ef4444; }
        .dot.yellow { background: #f59e0b; }
        .dot.green { background: #10b981; }

        .window-url {
            margin-left: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--muted);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            padding: 4px 14px;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .window-content {
            display: flex;
            height: 340px;
        }

        .mock-sidebar {
            width: 200px;
            background: #0d0d22;
            border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 16px 0;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .mock-server {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .mock-avatar {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--purple);
        }

        .mock-text { width: 80px; height: 10px; background: #1e1e4a; border-radius: 4px; }
        .mock-text.sm { width: 55px; height: 8px; background: #161637; margin-top: 4px; }

        .mock-nav-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--muted);
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .mock-nav-item.active {
            color: var(--purple-light);
            background: rgba(124,58,237,0.1);
            border-left: 2px solid var(--purple);
        }

        .mock-icon { width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 3px; background: currentColor; opacity: 0.4; }

        .mock-main {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .mock-title { width: 160px; height: 16px; background: #1e1e4a; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .mock-subtitle { width: 260px; height: 10px; background: #161637; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 24px; }

        .mock-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .mock-card {
            background: #161637;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 14px;
        }

        .mock-card-title { width: 90px; height: 10px; background: #1e1e4a; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; }

        .mock-channel {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            padding: 6px 8px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .mock-channel-icon { width: 14px; height: 10px; background: var(--muted); border-radius: 2px; opacity: 0.5; }
        .mock-channel-name { width: 70px; height: 8px; background: #2a2a5a; border-radius: 3px; }

        .mock-role {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            padding: 6px 8px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .mock-role-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }
        .mock-role-name { width: 65px; height: 8px; background: #2a2a5a; border-radius: 3px; }

        /* Features */
        .features {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 80px;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: var(--card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 28px 24px;
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }

        .feature-card:hover { border-color: rgba(124,58,237,0.4); }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            nav { padding: 16px 20px; }
            .features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .window-content { height: 200px; }
            .mock-sidebar { display: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">Set<span>cord</span></div>
        <a href="/auth/discord">Login with Discord</a>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="badge">⚡ Discord Server Management</div>
        <h1>Manage your Discord<br><span>server like a pro</span></h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Create channels, manage roles, and organize your server structure — all from a clean web dashboard.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="/auth/discord" class="btn-primary">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.317 4.37a19.791 19.791 0 0 0-4.885-1.515.074.074 0 0 0-.079.037c-.21.375-.444.864-.608 1.25a18.27 18.27 0 0 0-5.487 0 12.64 12.64 0 0 0-.617-1.25.077.077 0 0 0-.079-.037A19.736 19.736 0 0 0 3.677 4.37a.07.07 0 0 0-.032.027C.533 9.046-.32 13.58.099 18.057c.012.127.073.248.183.347 2.063 1.518 4.064 2.44 6.028 3.048a.078.078 0 0 0 .084-.028c.462-.63.874-1.295 1.226-1.994a.076.076 0 0 0-.041-.106 13.107 13.107 0 0 1-1.872-.892.077.077 0 0 1-.008-.128 10.2 10.2 0 0 0 .372-.292.074.074 0 0 1 .077-.01c3.928 1.793 8.18 1.793 12.062 0a.074.074 0 0 1 .078.01c.12.098.246.198.373.292a.077.077 0 0 1-.006.127 12.299 12.299 0 0 1-1.873.892.077.077 0 0 0-.041.107c.36.698.772 1.362 1.225 1.993a.076.076 0 0 0 .084.028 19.839 19.839 0 0 0 6.002-3.048.077.077 0 0 0 .032-.027c.5-5.177-.838-9.674-3.549-13.66a.061.061 0 0 0-.031-.03z"/></svg>
                Login with Discord
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com" class="btn-secondary" target="_blank">
                View on GitHub →
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Dashboard Preview -->
    <div class="preview">
        <div class="preview-window">
            <div class="window-bar">
                <div class="dot red"></div>
                <div class="dot yellow"></div>
                <div class="dot green"></div>
                <div class="window-url">localhost:3000/dashboard/channels</div>
            </div>
            <div class="window-content">
                <div class="mock-sidebar">
                    <div class="mock-server">
                        <div class="mock-avatar"></div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="mock-text"></div>
                            <div class="mock-text sm"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:12px;"></div>
                    <div class="mock-nav-item"><div class="mock-icon"></div> Dashboard</div>
                    <div class="mock-nav-item active"><div class="mock-icon"></div> Channels</div>
                    <div class="mock-nav-item"><div class="mock-icon"></div> Roles</div>
                    <div class="mock-nav-item"><div class="mock-icon"></div> Templates</div>
                    <div class="mock-nav-item"><div class="mock-icon"></div> Analytics</div>
                </div>
                <div class="mock-main">
                    <div class="mock-title"></div>
                    <div class="mock-subtitle"></div>
                    <div class="mock-grid">
                        <div class="mock-card">
                            <div class="mock-card-title"></div>
                            <div class="mock-channel"><div class="mock-channel-icon"></div><div class="mock-channel-name"></div></div>
                            <div class="mock-channel"><div class="mock-channel-icon"></div><div class="mock-channel-name" style="width:50px"></div></div>
                            <div class="mock-channel"><div class="mock-channel-icon"></div><div class="mock-channel-name" style="width:85px"></div></div>
                            <div class="mock-channel"><div class="mock-channel-icon"></div><div class="mock-channel-name" style="width:60px"></div></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mock-card">
                            <div class="mock-card-title"></div>
                            <div class="mock-role"><div class="mock-role-dot" style="background:#ef4444"></div><div class="mock-role-name"></div></div>
                            <div class="mock-role"><div class="mock-role-dot" style="background:#10b981"></div><div class="mock-role-name" style="width:50px"></div></div>
                            <div class="mock-role"><div class="mock-role-dot" style="background:#7c3aed"></div><div class="mock-role-name" style="width:75px"></div></div>
                            <div class="mock-role"><div class="mock-role-dot" style="background:#f59e0b"></div><div class="mock-role-name" style="width:45px"></div></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features -->
    <div class="features">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">💬</div>
            <h3>Channel Manager</h3>
            <p>Create, rename, delete text and voice channels. Organize them into categories with drag-and-drop ease.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
            <h3>Roles Manager</h3>
            <p>Build and customize your role hierarchy. Set colors, manage permissions, and assign roles to members.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔐</div>
            <h3>Secure by Design</h3>
            <p>Every action verifies your Discord permissions server-side. Your tokens never touch the client.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Setcord — Built with discord.js &amp; Express</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
